      • translate

        public Block translate(CodeSignature where,
                       Block continuation)
        Translates this expression into its intermediate Kitten code. The result is a piece of code which pushes onto the stack the value of expression, provided that it has the specified type. The original stack elements are not modified. Namely, it generates the code which starts with

        translation of expression
        cast from expression.getStaticType() into getStaticType()

        and continues with the given continuation.
        Specified by:
        translate in class Expression
        Parameters:
        where - the method or constructor where this expression occurs
        continuation - the code executed after this expression
        Returns:
        the code which evaluates this expression and continues with continuation
